divs: Sighting Detailsi was standing by my shed and looking up in the north sky at a bright star just before dusk but it was still light outside.and noticed slightly to the right of the star i saw something like a large blackdoorway whith silvery objects going in to it and some objects coming out.It only lasted for about a minute or less. then the black rectangle shifted sideways then dissappeared. this happened the next couple of nights,then suddenly stopped.
Summary: i was at my old house at the time looking at the first star in the north and slightly to the right of it i noticed just before dusk a blackdoorway, a rectangle and it appeared that some type of objects silvery in color were flying in and out of this area
